ReportQuery.ReportQueryText:
<QueryBundle> <QueryText>select z.* from ( select hc.CompanyName ,hp.PenNumber ,drop_trans.ReportDate ,AvgPenCount = convert(real, AVG(drop_trans.PenCount)) ,WAvgPenCount = convert(real, ISNULL(SUM(drop_trans.DropAFOz) / NULLIF(SUM(drop_trans.DropAFOzHd), 0), 0)) ,DropAF_MQty = dbo.GetMeasurementValue(SUM(drop_trans.DropAFOz), cmp.MediumMeasurementType) ,DropDM_MQty = dbo.GetMeasurementValue(SUM(drop_trans.DropDMOz), cmp.MediumMeasurementType) ,DropAF_MQty_PerHead = dbo.GetMeasurementValue(SUM(drop_trans.DropAFOzHd), cmp.MediumMeasurementType) ,DropDM_MQty_PerHead = dbo.GetMeasurementValue(SUM(drop_trans.DropDMOzHd), cmp.MediumMeasurementType) from ( select hp.HistoryPenGID ,hdl.HistoryLocationGID ,ReportDate = fs.InstanceDate ,PenCount = pcc.[Count] ,drop_trans.DropAFOz ,drop_trans.DropDMOz ,DropAFOzHd = ISNULL(drop_trans.DropAFOz / NULLIF(pcc.[Count], 0), 0) ,DropDMOzHd = ISNULL(drop_trans.DropDMOz / NULLIF(pcc.[Count], 0), 0) from FeedingScheduleDrop fsd join ( select it.TransactionSourceGID ,it.ToHistoryLocationGID ,it.FromHistoryLocationGID ,it.TransactionType ,StartDT = DATEADD(SECOND, -it.DurationSeconds, it.TransactionDT) ,StopDT = it.TransactionDT ,DropAFOz = SUM(it.UnitQuantity) ,DropDMOz = SUM(it.UnitQuantity * it.DMPct) from InventoryTransaction it where it.TransactionType in (1,5) group by it.TransactionSourceGID ,it.ToHistoryLocationGID ,it.FromHistoryLocationGID ,it.TransactionType ,it.TransactionDT ,it.DurationSeconds) drop_trans on fsd.FeedingScheduleDropGID = drop_trans.TransactionSourceGID join FeedingScheduleLoad fsl on fsl.FeedingScheduleLoadGID = fsd.FeedingScheduleLoadGID join FeedingScheduleMix fsm on fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID = fsl.FeedingScheduleMixGID join FeedingSchedule fs on fs.FeedingScheduleGID = fsm.FeedingScheduleGID join Pen pn on pn.LocationGID = fsd.LocationGID join PenCountChange pcc on pcc.PenCountChangeGID = (select top 1 pcc.PenCountChangeGID from PenCountChange pcc where pcc.PenGID = pn.PenGID and pcc.InventoryItemType = 3 and pcc.CreatedDT <= drop_trans.StartDT order by pcc.CreatedDT desc) join HistoryPen hp on hp.HistoryPenGID = (select top 1 hp.HistoryPenGID from HistoryPen hp where hp.PenGID = pn.PenGID and hp.CreatedDT <= drop_trans.StartDT order by hp.CreatedDT desc) join HistoryLocation hdl on hdl.HistoryLocationGID = drop_trans.ToHistoryLocationGID ) drop_trans join HistoryPen hp on hp.HistoryPenGID = drop_trans.HistoryPenGID join HistoryLocation hl on hl.HistoryLocationGID = drop_trans.HistoryLocationGID join HistoryCompany hc on hc.HistoryCompanyGID = hl.HistoryCompanyGID join Location loc on loc.LocationGID = hl.LocationGID join Company cmp on cmp.CompanyGID = loc.CompanyGID
group by hc.CompanyName, hp.PenNumber, drop_trans.ReportDate, cmp.MediumMeasurementType ) z where (1=1)</QueryText> <PreQueryText /> </QueryBundle>
ReportQuery.SQLStatement: select coalesce(hp1.PenNumber, hp2.PenNumber) as 'PenNumber' ,z.ReportDate ,AVG(pcc.[Count]) as 'AvgPenCount' ,SUM(z.DropAF_MQty) as 'DropAF_MQty' ,SUM(z.DropAF_MQty / nullif(pcc.[Count], 0)) as 'DropAF_MQty_Head' ,SUM(z.DropDM_MQty) as 'DropDM_MQty' ,SUM(z.DropDM_MQty / nullif(pcc.[Count], 0)) as 'DropDM_MQty_Head' from ( select fsd.LocationGID ,it.ToHistoryLocationGID ,p.PenGID ,it.TransactionDT ,case when CONVERT(time, it.TransactionDT) < hc.DayStartTime then CONVERT(date, dateadd(day, -1, it.TransactionDT)) else CONVERT(date, it.TransactionDT) end as 'ReportDate' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(SUM(it.UnitQuantity), hc.MediumMeasurementType) as DropAF_MQty ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(SUM(it.UnitQuantity * it.DMPct), hc.MediumMeasurementType) as DropDM_MQty from FeedingScheduleDrop fsd join InventoryTransaction it on it.TransactionSourceGID = fsd.FeedingScheduleDropGID join Pen p on p.LocationGID = fsd.LocationGID join HistoryLocation thl on thl.HistoryLocationGID = it.ToHistoryLocationGID join HistoryCompany hc on hc.HistoryCompanyGID = thl.HistoryCompanyGID group by fsd.LocationGID ,p.PenGID ,hc.MediumMeasurementType ,hc.DayStartTime ,it.TransactionDT ,it.ToHistoryLocationGID ) z cross apply (select top 1 pcc.[Count] from PenCountChange pcc where pcc.PenGID = z.PenGID and pcc.CreatedDT <= z.TransactionDT order by pcc.CreatedDT desc) pcc outer apply (select top 1 hp.* from HistoryPen hp where hp.PenGID = z.PenGID and hp.CreatedDT <= z.TransactionDT order by hp.CreatedDT desc) hp1 outer apply (select top 1 hp.* from HistoryPen hp where hp.PenGID = z.PenGID order by hp.CreatedDT) hp2 where (1=1) group by coalesce(hp1.PenNumber, hp2.PenNumber), z.ReportDate
